With this respect, we maintain that our morphometric, lithological, and structural covariates ( Table 2 ) are sound, accurate, and meaningful landslide predictors, and that they contribute to explain the known spatio-temporal distribution of landslides in our ( Fig. 1 ) and in similar study areas.
